<section class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-950 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-14 sm:py-20 text-center">
  <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-yellow-100 dark:bg-yellow-900/30 text-yellow-700 dark:text-yellow-400 text-xs font-semibold mb-6 font-mono-highlight tracking-wide uppercase">
    <span>✈</span> Do Aeroporto para o Mundo
  </div>

  <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-50 leading-tight">
    Aviões do <span class="hero-highlight">Deploy</span>
  </h1>

  <p class="mt-5 text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
    Time pequeno, ideias grandes. Aprendemos na marra, construímos
    soluções leves e crescemos juntos — de eventos a projetos reais.
  </p>

  <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-3 sm:gap-4">
    <a
      href="https://discord.gg/Pbmssyrv"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-md bg-yellow-300 text-slate-900 font-semibold hover:bg-yellow-200 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow-400 focus:ring-offset-2 dark:focus:ring-offset-slate-950"
    >
      <i class="bi bi-chat-square-text" aria-hidden="true"></i>
      Junte-se à comunidade
    </a>
    <a
      href="./manifesto"
      class="w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-md border-2 border-slate-900 dark:border-slate-50 text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-50 font-semibold hover:bg-slate-900 hover:text-white dark:hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:text-slate-900 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-slate-900 dark:focus:ring-slate-50 focus:ring-offset-2 dark:focus:ring-offset-slate-950"
    >
      <i class="bi bi-file-text" aria-hidden="true"></i>
      Ver manifesto
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- Logo illustration -->
  <div class="mt-12 sm:mt-14">
    <img
      src="./favicon.webp"
      alt="Aviões do Deploy"
      class="w-32 h-32 sm:w-48 sm:h-48 mx-auto object-contain rounded-full"
    />
  </div>
</section>

